data.meta_description: Conrad I of Swabia was born about 925 in Elsass, Germany / Alsace, France. He was married  to Richlint von Sachsen, of Saxony, they had 4 children. He was married  to Judith von Marchtal, they gave birth to 1 child. He died on August 20, 997 in Elsass, Germany / Alsace, France. This information is part of Family Tree Welborn by Marvin Loyd Welborn on Genealogy Online.
